INSERT INTO Articles VALUES("23","3","Last Night In Pasadena / Wednesday, May 27th","<p>It is with sadness that I announce Wednesday, May 27th as my last night teaching a weekly class at Family Dance Studio in Pasadena. Earlier this year when I was asked to come on board by owners Francisco and Stacey Martinez I was very excited but we all knew logistics might not work out long-term (plans on paper don\'t always work out in real life, LOL. After two months of trying to fit the weekly drive into my schedule, it has become clear that it\'s best to discontinue the classes. Nonetheless, I want to thank Francisco and Stacey for the opportunity, I have nothing but the utmost respect for them and for the staff at Dance Family Studio, and the students are WONDERFUL. And, even though I won\'t be there on Wednesday nights anymore, I hope to see you all at the West Coast Swing Bootcamp sponsored by DFS this coming<br />Saturday, May 30th (see below for details).</p>","1244495003","Jun","2009","Article");
INSERT INTO Articles VALUES("26","3","Sub for Sunday, June 21","<p>Hello, everyone!</p>\n<p>I am out of town this coming weekend, celebrating the birthday of the very fabulous David Walkup. We have plans for a hot air balloon ride, a limo-driven tour of local Temecula wineries, dinner and dancing, what a great way to celebrate such a special day!&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, back at the ranch, despite my absence THERE WILL BE CLASS ON SUNDAY, JUNE 21ST!</p>\n<p>The very capable Mike Kluck will be subbing for all four Sunday classes, EVEN the 5:00 pm American Tango class.</p>\n<p>In addition to all of Mike\'s WCS experience, he\'s also been taking AND teaching Ballroom at the new You Can Dance Studio in Hermosa Beach (remember that great dance party a few weeks ago?), so you will be in very capable hands (you know I wouldn\'t leave you with just anyone, LOL).&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Brian P will be working the registration desk as usual so you will see his familiar face. Have a great day and enjoy Mike Kluck!</p>\n<p>SCHEDULE</p>\n<p>2:00 pm - Beginning WCS - WE NEED MORE NEWBIES! Bring us your newbie friends!</p>\n<p>3:00 pm - Beyond Basics WCS</p>\n<p>4:00 pm - Inter/Adv WCS</p>\n<p>5:00 pm - Beginning Ballroom: American Tango</p>\n<p>Double H Club/Hacienda Hotel</p>\n<p>525 North Sepulveda Blvd.</p>\n<p>El Segundo, 90245</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","1245367138","Jun","2009","Article");
INSERT INTO Articles VALUES("27","3","WE NEED YOUR DANCE NEWBIES","<p>We need your dance newbies NOW!!</p>\n<p>Bring in your dance newbies to the Dance Chatte Hacienda &amp; Burbank classes.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If your referral signs up for a 6-Week Series, YOU get a discount on your next paid series!</p>\n<p>Anyway, make sure your friends, neighbors, family, co-workers who have asked you about dance know we have beginning level classes in TWO locations:</p>\n<p>Sundays/Hacienda</p>\n<p>2:00pm Beginning WCS</p>\n<p>5:00 pm - Beginning Ballroom: American Tango</p>\n<p>TUESDAYS/ Burbank</p>\n<p>7:30 pm - Beginning WCS</p>\n<p>9:00 pm - Beginning &amp; Beyond Country 2-Step</p>\n<p>Let\'s get those newbies dancing! Drink the koolaid, folks! Soylent Green is PEOPLE! (j/k)</p>\n<p>t</p>","1245367493","Jun","2009","Article");
