ill also include TWO buffet meals with the event pass &ndash; that mean two meals you don&rsquo;t have to bring yourself from home (cold squished sandwich, anyone?) or two over-priced restaurant meals you&rsquo;d have to buy elsewhere, so that&rsquo;s a great deal. </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua,palatino;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; And, if you do the J&amp;J competing thing, make sure you check out B&amp;K&rsquo;s J&amp;J club contest with different qualifying rounds around town this month and next leading up to the finals at the event, and they have some awesome prizes, too! Check out the list of qualifying events and make sure you attend Paradise!</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua,palatino;\">www.magicdanceproductions.com/paradisecountrydance.html<br /></span></span></span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","1251225773","Aug","2009","Article");
