INSERT INTO Articles VALUES("59","23","CruiseFest Update","<p><!--StartFragment--></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 26.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Marker Felt&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\">CruiseFest Swing Dance Cruise</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">UPDATE FROM DANCE FUN CRUISE DIRECTOR </span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">JOHN RIDDLE</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>We\'re about 6 months out from <strong><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">our CruiseFest Swing Dance Cruise</em></strong> and 3 months till Final Payment is due.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>While we can continue to book passage all the way up to September, on May 21st our remaining block of cabins reverts back to Carnival. After that point we can still book passages but we can not guarantee what Carnival will do with the pricing.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Last year Carnival was in trouble (the economy, etc.) and the price dropped a bit and we passed on that price reduction to those that had already booked. But, according to Carnival they are in good shape as far as sales for this year&rsquo;s cruise.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>With that in mind, odds are there will be a slight increase in cost after May 21<sup>st</sup>!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Dancers, if you\'re considering the cruise... </span></span></em></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">NOW</span></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"> is the time to book! </span></span></em></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\">You only need a small deposit and will have months to pay on the balance.</span></em></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Don\'t miss out! Last year was a <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">blast</em>, cabins for this year are going fast.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Come sail and party with Dance Instructors: ???Skippy Blair, Samantha Buckwalter, Kelly Casanova, <strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">Trish Connery &amp; David Walkup</span></strong>, Patti Jobst, Michael Kielbasa, Ben Morris &amp; Melina Ramirez, Martin Parker and ???DJ Jumpin&rsquo; Jack Smith! </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The Cruise leaves from Galveston, Texas headed for the Western Caribbean &ndash; 7 Days and 7 Nights. Ports of call include Montego Bay, Jamaica; Grand Cayman; and Cozumel, Mexico.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Cabin prices include <strong><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">ALL</em></strong> CruiseFest Dances, Workshops, Food, Beverages (alcoholic beverages not included), ship&rsquo;s entertainment and activities, all for a little over a $100 a day. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\">$749.00/Inside, $849.00/Ocean View, $1049.00/Private Balcony</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\">*$51.31 additional government taxes </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\">*Prices are per person and based on double occupancy in a cabin</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\">DON\'T FORGET TO MENTION MY NAME</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\">TRISH CONNERY!</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"> John Riddle, Dance Fun &amp; CruiseFest Swing Dance Cruise</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;; color: #333333;\"> 866-326-2338???405-282-8989</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","1273020162","May","2010","Article");



